1. *Rame* mi je veoma bolno. (My *shoulder* hurts a lot.)
2. Stavila je ruku na moje *rame*. (She put her hand on my *shoulder*.)
3. Ukoliko nosite torbu na jednom *ramenu*, možete izazvati bolove u leđima. (If you carry a bag on one *shoulder*, you can cause back pain.)
4. *Rame* na kojem sam plakala je sada već suvo. (The *shoulder* on which I cried is now dry.)
5. Duga kosa joj je prekrivala *rame*. (Her long hair covered her *shoulder*.)
6. Hteo je da je izvede u ples, ali se ona povukla i rekla da joj boli *rame*. (He wanted to take her dancing, but she withdrew and said her *shoulder* hurt.)
7. *Rame* za plakanje uvek ćeš imati kod mene. (You'll always have a *shoulder* to cry on with me.)
8. Ova bluza ima otvorenih *ramena*. (This blouse has open *shoulders*.)
9. Ona je veoma jaka i može da podigne tegove od 100 kilograma na jednom *ramenu*. (She's very strong and can lift 100-kilogram weights on one *shoulder*.)
10. Lepota joj je bila teret koji je nosila na svojim *ramenima*. (Beauty was the burden she carried on her *shoulders*.)